# Triangular prism for prism turret (zzw mod)
# 3-sided prism, height along Y axis, triangle in XZ plane
# Has normals (vn) for proper backface culling and normalAngle shading
# All faces are quads (triangles converted to degenerate quads) to avoid
# WavefrontObject's deferred Draw.draw(z, face::draw) which causes vertex
# mutation bugs when multiple prism turrets render simultaneously.
o Prism
v 0.800000 -1.000000 0.000000
v -0.400000 -1.000000 0.692820
v -0.400000 -1.000000 -0.692820
v 0.800000 1.000000 0.000000
v -0.400000 1.000000 0.692820
v -0.400000 1.000000 -0.692820
vn 0.000000 -1.000000 0.000000
vn 0.000000 1.000000 0.000000
vn 0.498000 0.000000 0.867000
vn -1.000000 0.000000 0.000000
vn 0.498000 0.000000 -0.867000
# bottom face (degenerate quad: triangle with duplicated last vertex)
f 3//1 2//1 1//1 1//1
# top face (degenerate quad)
f 4//2 5//2 6//2 6//2
# side faces (quads)
f 1//3 4//3 5//3 2//3
f 2//4 5//4 6//4 3//4
f 3//5 6//5 4//5 1//5
